Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.62,0:00:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.51,0:00:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么想搞的话你自己一个人搞好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.21,0:00:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.46,0:00:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太喜欢把自己的爱好强加于人了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.18,0:00:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢 我们没法像你那么当回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.14,0:00:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说只是同人志而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.22,0:00:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要把截稿期定得那么严啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.30,0:00:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人逼着写一点都不好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.52,0:00:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.31,0:00:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 以后你自己写吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.61,0:00:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.86,0:02:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 时间到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.58,0:02:38.75,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 第四题的答案是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.12,0:02:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再动笔了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.12,0:02:42.09,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓了吧 反正考完试就放暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.22,0:02:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把答题纸扣在桌子上 最后边的同学收上来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.59,0:02:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三十分以下的要补习的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.69,0:02:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要注意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.21,0:02:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.31,0:02:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 已经晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.91,0:02:58.65,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(全百合题材同人志即卖会 百合祭)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.87,0:02:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了我真的要补习了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.06,0:03:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 今天还有社团活动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.70,0:03:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BYEBYE
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.45,0:03:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BYEBYE
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小~纯~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.16,0:03:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天大家一起对对答案怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.30,0:03:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.33,0:03:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?啊 苍井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.67,0:03:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次说的事 你有考虑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.13,0:03:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶? 上次说的? 什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.78,0:03:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.06,0:03:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全百合题材同人志的即卖会 百合祭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.05,0:03:43.75,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们 [织野真纱香传道会] 也拿到席位了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.05,0:03:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.07,0:03:47.07,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上纪念<傍晚>的第一期
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.36,0:03:49.66,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出了哦 新刊!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.73,0:03:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风...风间?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.81,0:04:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样居然都能完成对话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.82,0:04:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那个大脑门居然没有察觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.56,0:04:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我也回家写原稿了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把落下的全补回来哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.76,0:04:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.39,0:05:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假打算去哪打工
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.01,0:05:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有啊 在空调房里睡觉就能拿千元时薪的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.82,0:05:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.28,0:05:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们凡夫俗子就请过个浑浑噩噩的暑假吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.49,0:05:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的夏天...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.32,0:05:29.27,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}(我的暑假)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和村雨同学一起制作了同人志
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.26,0:05:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去村雨同学家留宿了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.80,0:05:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去参加了EVENT
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.59,0:05:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.82,0:05:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.07,0:05:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该多好啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.27,0:05:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 你回来了 梓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.59,0:05:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.41,0:05:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你看下店
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.00,0:05:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶? 为什么? 妈妈呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.31,0:06:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去医院了 你奶奶那里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚考试完应该很闲的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.87,0:06:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有我的事要做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.18,0:06:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.39,0:06:15.89,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(酒 苍井)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.76,0:06:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.56,0:06:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.65,0:06:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 也罢...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.52,0:06:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.74,0:06:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天也没有适合思考的环境啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.82,0:06:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考试既然已经顺利结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也该正式考虑下活动的问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活动是指...什么活动?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.46,0:06:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考试把你考傻了吗 村雨君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.54,0:06:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是说女子部了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.92,0:06:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还没有放弃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:07:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋绘的字典里没有放弃两个字哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.70,0:07:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来里边缺的不光是这两个字啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.22,0:07:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,申请被驳回
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.93,0:07:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山崎明美君也不见人影
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 明美到底跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.85,0:07:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像烟一样飘散了啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.03,0:07:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的幽灵部员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.33,0:07:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋绘 这词用的太准确了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.62,0:07:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们女子部现在迎来了成立以来的最大危机
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.46,0:07:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生一起享受放学后时光的目的就无法实现
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.79,0:07:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们这样不算吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.21,0:07:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说多少次你才明白 村雨君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中生当然要参加社团活动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.14,0:07:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.63,0:07:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.35,0:07:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你说什么都没用 我已经完全明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.43,0:07:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是朋绘的优点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.87,0:07:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优点啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.19,0:08:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我又去邀请过鸟追君...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.52,0:08:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒绝 哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.94,0:08:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候的事?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.95,0:08:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 别再让小清为难了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.41,0:08:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部员人数的问题我们今后再慢慢商量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.54,0:08:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.54,0:08:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了加强我们的团结我有一个提案
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.92,0:08:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.88,0:08:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.80,0:08:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,季节是夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.18,0:08:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到夏天...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.85,0:08:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然要合宿!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.57,0:08:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨同学家的宅子好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.82,0:08:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有家政妇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.55,0:08:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来也一定有别墅吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊 如果她邀请我的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊 好美的星空
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.63,0:09:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我们两个简直就像飘在宇宙中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.56,0:09:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀~真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.31,0:09:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年夏天是不是搞些原创呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.31,0:09:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.90,0:09:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个也许不错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.57,0:09:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:34.36,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}(有钱人家的大小姐与酒贩的女儿)\N(来到避暑地少女与当地酒厂的女孩)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.95,0:09:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是二次创作 而是自己的原创小说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.06,0:09:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原型人物一看就知道是谁也不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.72,0:09:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原创到底该怎么写才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.51,0:09:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是第一次参展 还是二次创作比较容易吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.68,0:10:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然也许写不好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.29,0:10:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我多努力一下的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.63,0:10:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨同学也会觉得更有干劲的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.93,0:10:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是第一次和朋友一起做的书
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.88,0:10:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.02,0:10:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓在房间里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.51,0:10:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.85,0:10:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考试不是已经结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.94,0:10:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个吧 同人志
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.71,0:10:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来 她说找到了同好 高兴得不得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.03,0:10:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来很担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.66,0:10:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看她上了高中也交不到朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 看来已经不用担心了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.52,0:11:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合宿就定在八月六日了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.52,0:11:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶? 等等等等等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.77,0:11:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要搞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.07,0:11:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是早就说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.94,0:11:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你考试能得全年级第一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.66,0:11:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记性居然这么差
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.16,0:11:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为部员太没自觉性了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家部才不会搞什么合宿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是告诉过你是女子部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.44,0:11:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 好好打扫卫生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.36,0:11:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也别擅自定下来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.85,0:11:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有我的安排
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.09,0:11:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.68,0:12:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.94,0:12:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要去的是海边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想象一下 说到海边...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.15,0:12:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.16,0:12:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小纯~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.05,0:12:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在~...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.54,0:12:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是想象 是妄想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.05,0:12:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛...嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去就去一次吧 合宿 大夏天的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.68,0:12:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小纯?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.30,0:12:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得好快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.05,0:12:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海边啊 真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.74,0:13:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时间的话 鸟追君也来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.37,0:13:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.12,0:13:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候要是没有别的事就去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.16,0:13:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 去年的泳装还能穿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.41,0:13:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.67,0:13:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.50,0:13:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天一起去买泳装吧 放学以后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.26,0:13:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.98,0:13:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明显是别有用心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.93,0:13:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.97,0:13:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫别有用心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.66,0:13:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.77,0:13:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是说一起去买泳装而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是在妄想什么变态的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.25,0:13:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.27,0:13:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想骗我 你那野兽般的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.74,0:13:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得这样一个机会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.45,0:13:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然给她看看完成的作品 给她个惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.05,0:14:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许受到这个刺激 村雨同学也会写个原创呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.68,0:14:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.78,0:14:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不是真纱香姐姐大人的同人志了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 也罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.88,0:14:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.41,0:14:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假都还没有开始 居然就这么开心...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.55,0:14:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好啦!太好啦!完成啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.72,0:14:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一作完全自创的小说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.98,0:14:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 我该怎么办啊 真不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.64,0:14:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且每张两页 每页一千二百字 一共五十张
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.61,0:14:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样出copy志好像有点不大可行了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.61,0:14:53.83,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}(copy志 就是自家的复印机打印机打出来装订成册的同人志 字数太多的话成本会很高)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.50,0:14:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试试? 要试试吗? 登上大人的阶梯...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:14:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,offset...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:14:59.79,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}(offset志 就是在印刷厂印刷的同人志)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.53,0:15:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 回头再想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.79,0:15:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先睡一觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.42,0:15:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 过两小时就要去上学了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.68,0:15:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 标题...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.10,0:15:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.33,0:15:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向日葵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.58,0:15:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向日葵的花语是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.00,0:15:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凝视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.76,0:15:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶? 我也要做什么吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.49,0:15:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不记得吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.08,0:15:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是刚考完试时候...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.59,0:15:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊啊 那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.63,0:16:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 那时候刚考完试累得有点迷糊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.35,0:16:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都坐好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.88,0:16:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发通信簿了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.93,0:16:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等下再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.69,0:16:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不叫通信簿了啊 最近...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.75,0:16:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.14,0:16:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.55,0:16:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}{\fs15}就\N是\N说\N\N那\N么\N想\N搞\N的\N话\N你\N自\N己\N一\N个\N人\N搞\N好\N了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.97,0:16:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\fs15}直\N说\N吧\N\N你\N太\N喜\N欢\N把\N自\N己\N的\N爱\N好\N强\N加\N于\N人\N了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.36,0:16:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}{\fs15}同人志而已 为什么要把截稿期定得那么严
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.61,0:17:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍井同学...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.09,0:17:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别迟到了哦 你迟到了连我都得挨训
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶? 几点来着?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.71,0:17:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九点啊九点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.25,0:17:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是十点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.17,0:17:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是开店的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.89,0:17:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么九点就去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.30,0:17:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备开店啦 打扫卫生啦 该做的事多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.43,0:17:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.77,0:17:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍井同学已经回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.46,0:17:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.09,0:18:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人的暑假 又不是第一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.64,0:18:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 你回来了 梓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.39,0:18:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 没考好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她爸爸 啤酒不够了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.43,0:18:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 梓 你回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.10,0:19:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊对了 叫什么来着 那个EVENT
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.53,0:19:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年不是要和朋友一起去的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.53,0:19:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带她来家里玩玩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.48,0:19:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.20,0:20:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 这房间好乱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.16,0:20:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么你的朋友全都是这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.04,0:20:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.38,0:20:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像 做了件很过分的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.86,0:20:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即然这样想 尽力挽回就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.54,0:20:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我睡着了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.62,0:20:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 大开着窗户
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.54,0:20:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭声都被邻居听到了...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.01,0:20:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.82,0:21:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同学...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.16,0:21:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.91,0:21:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨同学? 你怎么在这?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.76,0:23:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 这个印成书后打算怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.05,0:23:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说村雨同学 这你都不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.86,0:23:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个啊这个
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.39,0:23:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全百合题材同人志即卖会 百合祭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.77,0:23:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YAHOO
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.11,0:23:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创作Parody
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.24,0:23:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二次元也好三次元也好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.53,0:23:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管水平如何都能进入的百合解放区
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.03,0:23:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣地有明只有这个日子男人免进
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.03,0:23:22.96,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}(有明是同人Event举办地 著名的东京国际展示场在有明)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.25,0:23:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年两次的少女祭典哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.57,0:23:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.27,0:23:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 八月六日?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.63,0:23:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周就去海边啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.90,0:23:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.46,0:23:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.14,0:23:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了这个日子 我把驾照都考下来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅~
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.85,0:23:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么有不好的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.93,0:23:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀? 好奇怪啊 引擎怎么...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.76,0:23:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GOGO!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.53,0:23:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.75,0:23:50.70,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一话 [Happening In Summer]


